scenes.description: Compilation of "Capture the Moment" message boards featuring notes from hololive talents and fans.
Event precautions and attendee information slides in Japanese and English.
Showcase of official merchandise for hololive 5th fes., including penlights and apparel.
Official merchandise sales schedule for on-site and post-event online sales.
Continued compilation of message boards from the hololive community.
